{
  "video_id": "LIy2oVJtJsA",
  "title": "Krista Donaldson: The $80 prosthetic knee that's changing lives",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12982.0,
      "end_time": 14602.0,
      "text": "Nine years ago, I worked"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14602.0,
      "end_time": 16799.0,
      "text": "for the U.S. government in Iraq,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16799.0,
      "end_time": 19928.0,
      "text": "helping rebuild the electricity infrastructure."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19928.0,
      "end_time": 22565.0,
      "text": "And I was there, and I worked in that job"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22565.0,
      "end_time": 24415.0,
      "text": "because I believe that technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24415.0,
      "end_time": 27640.0,
      "text": "can improve people&#39;s lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27640.0,
      "end_time": 29999.0,
      "text": "One afternoon, I had tea with a storekeeper"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 29999.0,
      "end_time": 32818.0,
      "text": "at the Al Rasheed Hotel in Baghdad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32819.0,
      "end_time": 35558.0,
      "text": "and he said to me, \"You Americans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35558.0,
      "end_time": 36909.0,
      "text": "you can put a man on the moon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 36909.0,
      "end_time": 38454.0,
      "text": "but when I get home tonight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 38454.0,
      "end_time": 41310.0,
      "text": "I won&#39;t be able to turn on my lights.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 41310.0,
      "end_time": 42967.0,
      "text": "At the time, the U.S. government had spent"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 42967.0,
      "end_time": 45327.0,
      "text": "more than two billion dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 45327.0,
      "end_time": 47684.0,
      "text": "on electricity reconstruction."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 47684.0,
      "end_time": 50855.0,
      "text": "How do you ensure technology reaches users?"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 50856.0,
      "end_time": 52836.0,
      "text": "How do you put it in their hands"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 52836.0,
      "end_time": 55710.0,
      "text": "so that it is useful?"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 55720.0,
      "end_time": 58116.0,
      "text": "So those are the questions that my colleagues and I"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 58116.0,
      "end_time": 60229.0,
      "text": "at D-Rev ask ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 60229.0,
      "end_time": 63377.0,
      "text": "And D-Rev is short for Design Revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63377.0,
      "end_time": 65971.0,
      "text": "And I took over the organization four years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 65971.0,
      "end_time": 68272.0,
      "text": "and really focused it on developing products"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68272.0,
      "end_time": 70460.0,
      "text": "that actually reach users,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 70460.0,
      "end_time": 71946.0,
      "text": "and not just any users,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 71946.0,
      "end_time": 76100.0,
      "text": "but customers who live on less than four dollars a day."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 76100.0,
      "end_time": 77909.0,
      "text": "One of the key areas we&#39;ve been working on recently"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 77909.0,
      "end_time": 80422.0,
      "text": "is medical devices, and while it may not be obvious"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 80422.0,
      "end_time": 82554.0,
      "text": "that medical devices have something in common"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 82554.0,
      "end_time": 85120.0,
      "text": "with Iraq&#39;s electricity grid then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 85120.0,
      "end_time": 87249.0,
      "text": "there are some commonalities."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 87249.0,
      "end_time": 89958.0,
      "text": "Despite the advanced technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 89958.0,
      "end_time": 92726.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not reaching the people who need it most."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 92726.0,
      "end_time": 95134.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m going to tell you about one of the projects we&#39;ve been working on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 95134.0,
      "end_time": 98410.0,
      "text": "the ReMotion Knee, and it&#39;s a prosthetic knee"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 98410.0,
      "end_time": 100197.0,
      "text": "for above-knee amputees."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 100197.0,
      "end_time": 103497.0,
      "text": "And this project started when the Jaipur Foot Organization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 103497.0,
      "end_time": 106910.0,
      "text": "the largest fitter of prosthetic limbs in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 106910.0,
      "end_time": 107559.0,
      "text": "came to the Bay Area and they said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 107560.0,
      "end_time": 110530.0,
      "text": "\"We need a better knee.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 110530.0,
      "end_time": 113678.0,
      "text": "Chances are, if you&#39;re living on less than four dollars a day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 113678.0,
      "end_time": 115554.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;re an amputee,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 115555.0,
      "end_time": 117729.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ve lost your limb in a vehicle accident."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 117729.0,
      "end_time": 119142.0,
      "text": "Most people think it&#39;s land mines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 119142.0,
      "end_time": 120747.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s a vehicle accident."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 120748.0,
      "end_time": 122604.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re walking by the side of the road"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 122604.0,
      "end_time": 124280.0,
      "text": "and you&#39;re hit by a truck,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 124280.0,
      "end_time": 125889.0,
      "text": "or you&#39;re trying to to jump on a moving train,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 125889.0,
      "end_time": 129872.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re late for work, and your pant leg gets caught."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 129872.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133370.0,
      "text": "And the reality is that if you don&#39;t have much money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 133380.0,
      "end_time": 135380.0,
      "text": "like this young named Kamal right here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 135380.0,
      "end_time": 137242.0,
      "text": "the option you really have"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 137242.0,
      "end_time": 139805.0,
      "text": "is a bamboo staff to get around."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 139806.0,
      "end_time": 142289.0,
      "text": "And how big a problem is this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 142289.0,
      "end_time": 145214.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s over three million amputees every year"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 145215.0,
      "end_time": 148504.0,
      "text": "who need a new or replacement knee."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 148504.0,
      "end_time": 150373.0,
      "text": "And what are their options?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 150373.0,
      "end_time": 152971.0,
      "text": "This is a high-end. This is what we&#39;d call a \"smart knee.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 152972.0,
      "end_time": 154990.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s got a microprocessor inside."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 154990.0,
      "end_time": 157750.0,
      "text": "It can pretty much do anything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 157750.0,
      "end_time": 158772.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s 20,000 dollars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 158772.0,
      "end_time": 160977.0,
      "text": "and to give you a sense of who wears this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 160978.0,
      "end_time": 164221.0,
      "text": "veterans, American veterans coming back from Afghanistan or Iraq"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 164221.0,
      "end_time": 166547.0,
      "text": "would be fit with something like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 166547.0,
      "end_time": 169640.0,
      "text": "This is a low-end titanium knee."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 169640.0,
      "end_time": 171541.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a polycentric knee, and all that that means"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 171541.0,
      "end_time": 173750.0,
      "text": "is the mechanism, is a four-bar mechanism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 173750.0,
      "end_time": 176300.0,
      "text": "that mimics a natural human knee."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 176300.0,
      "end_time": 178703.0,
      "text": "But at 1,400 dollars, it&#39;s still too expensive"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 178703.0,
      "end_time": 181870.0,
      "text": "for people like Kamal."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 181870.0,
      "end_time": 183679.0,
      "text": "And lastly, here you see a low-end knee."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 183680.0,
      "end_time": 185511.0,
      "text": "This is a knee that&#39;s been designed specifically"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 185511.0,
      "end_time": 187186.0,
      "text": "for poor people."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 187187.0,
      "end_time": 189200.0,
      "text": "And while you have affordability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 189200.0,
      "end_time": 190915.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ve lost on functionality."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 190915.0,
      "end_time": 193566.0,
      "text": "The mechanism here is a single axis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 193566.0,
      "end_time": 195815.0,
      "text": "and a single axis is like a door hinge."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 195815.0,
      "end_time": 198100.0,
      "text": "So you can think about how unstable that would be."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 198100.0,
      "end_time": 200500.0,
      "text": "And this is the type of mechanism"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 200500.0,
      "end_time": 203894.0,
      "text": "that the Jaipur Foot Organization was using when they were looking for a better knee,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 203894.0,
      "end_time": 206251.0,
      "text": "and I just wanted to give you a sense of what a leg system looks like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 206251.0,
      "end_time": 207590.0,
      "text": "because I&#39;m showing you all these knees"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 207590.0,
      "end_time": 209966.0,
      "text": "and I imagine it&#39;s hard to think  how it all fits together."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 209966.0,
      "end_time": 212800.0,
      "text": "So at the top you have a socket,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 212800.0,
      "end_time": 213954.0,
      "text": "and this fits over someone&#39;s residual limb,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 213954.0,
      "end_time": 216514.0,
      "text": "and everyone&#39;s residual limb is a little bit different."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 216514.0,
      "end_time": 217698.0,
      "text": "And then you have the knee,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 217698.0,
      "end_time": 219416.0,
      "text": "and here I&#39;ve got a single axis on the knee"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 219416.0,
      "end_time": 221128.0,
      "text": "so you can see how it rotates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 221128.0,
      "end_time": 225900.0,
      "text": "and then a pylon, and then a foot."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 225910.0,
      "end_time": 227634.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;ve been able to develop a knee,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 227634.0,
      "end_time": 229995.0,
      "text": "a polycentric knee, so that type of knee"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 229996.0,
      "end_time": 232571.0,
      "text": "that acts like a human knee, mimics human gait,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 232571.0,
      "end_time": 235314.0,
      "text": "for 80 dollars retail."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 235314.0,
      "end_time": 238878.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 238878.0,
      "end_time": 241432.0,
      "text": "But the key is, you can have this great invention,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 241432.0,
      "end_time": 243417.0,
      "text": "you can have this great design, but how do you get it"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 243418.0,
      "end_time": 245190.0,
      "text": "to the people who most need it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 245190.0,
      "end_time": 248496.0,
      "text": "How do you ensure it gets to them and it improves their lives?"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 248496.0,
      "end_time": 251432.0,
      "text": "So at D-Rev, we&#39;ve done some other projects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 251432.0,
      "end_time": 253815.0,
      "text": "and we looked at three things that we really believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 253816.0,
      "end_time": 257788.0,
      "text": "gets technologies to customers, to users,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 257788.0,
      "end_time": 259164.0,
      "text": "to people who need it."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 259164.0,
      "end_time": 261885.0,
      "text": "And the first thing is that the product  needs to be world class."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 261885.0,
      "end_time": 263536.0,
      "text": "It needs to perform on par"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 263536.0,
      "end_time": 266381.0,
      "text": "or better than the best products on the market."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 266381.0,
      "end_time": 268527.0,
      "text": "Regardless of your income level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 268527.0,
      "end_time": 270650.0,
      "text": "you want the most beautiful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 270650.0,
      "end_time": 272753.0,
      "text": "the best product that there is."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 272753.0,
      "end_time": 276241.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to show you a video now"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 276242.0,
      "end_time": 277888.0,
      "text": "of a man named Ash. You can see him walking."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 277888.0,
      "end_time": 279799.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s wearing the same knee system here"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 279800.0,
      "end_time": 281406.0,
      "text": "with a single axis knee."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 281406.0,
      "end_time": 283498.0,
      "text": "And he&#39;s doing a 10-meter walk test."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 283498.0,
      "end_time": 287313.0,
      "text": "And you&#39;ll notice that he&#39;s struggling  with stability as he&#39;s walking."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 287313.0,
      "end_time": 289967.0,
      "text": "And something that&#39;s not obvious, that you can&#39;t see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 289968.0,
      "end_time": 292555.0,
      "text": "is that it&#39;s psychologically draining"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 292555.0,
      "end_time": 296337.0,
      "text": "to walk and to be preventing yourself from falling."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 296337.0,
      "end_time": 298410.0,
      "text": "Now this is a video of Kamal."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 298410.0,
      "end_time": 300774.0,
      "text": "You remember Kamal earlier, holding the bamboo staff."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 300774.0,
      "end_time": 303482.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s wearing one of the earlier versions of our knee,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 303482.0,
      "end_time": 306582.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;s doing that same 10-meter walk test."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 306582.0,
      "end_time": 309998.0,
      "text": "And you can see his stability is much better."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 311849.0,
      "end_time": 314968.0,
      "text": "So world class isn&#39;t just about technical performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 314968.0,
      "end_time": 318308.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also about human performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 318308.0,
      "end_time": 320166.0,
      "text": "And most medical devices, we&#39;ve learned,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 320166.0,
      "end_time": 322694.0,
      "text": "as we&#39;ve dug in, are really designed for Westerners,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 322694.0,
      "end_time": 324357.0,
      "text": "for wealthier economies."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 324357.0,
      "end_time": 327619.0,
      "text": "But the reality is our users, our customers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 327619.0,
      "end_time": 330172.0,
      "text": "they do different things. They sit cross-legged more."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 330172.0,
      "end_time": 333140.0,
      "text": "We see that they squat. They kneel in prayer."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 333140.0,
      "end_time": 335762.0,
      "text": "And we designed our knee to have the greatest range of motion"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 335762.0,
      "end_time": 339846.0,
      "text": "of almost any other knee on the market."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 339846.0,
      "end_time": 341576.0,
      "text": "So the second thing we learned, and this leads"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 341576.0,
      "end_time": 343836.0,
      "text": "into my second point, which is that we believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 343836.0,
      "end_time": 346553.0,
      "text": "that products need to be designed to be user-centric."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 346553.0,
      "end_time": 349153.0,
      "text": "And at D-Rev, we go one step further and we say"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 349153.0,
      "end_time": 351530.0,
      "text": "you need to be user-obsessed."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 351530.0,
      "end_time": 353773.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s not just the end user that you&#39;re thinking about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 353773.0,
      "end_time": 355749.0,
      "text": "but everyone who interacts with the product,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 355749.0,
      "end_time": 358463.0,
      "text": "so, for example, the prosthetist who fits the knee,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 358463.0,
      "end_time": 361631.0,
      "text": "but also the context in which the knee is being fit."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 361631.0,
      "end_time": 363215.0,
      "text": "What is the local market like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 363215.0,
      "end_time": 365133.0,
      "text": "How do all these components get to the clinic?"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 365133.0,
      "end_time": 367455.0,
      "text": "Do they all get there on time? The supply chain."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 367455.0,
      "end_time": 369558.0,
      "text": "Everything that goes into ensuring"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 369558.0,
      "end_time": 371541.0,
      "text": "that this product gets to the end user,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 371541.0,
      "end_time": 375962.0,
      "text": "and it goes in as part of the system, and it&#39;s used."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 375962.0,
      "end_time": 377828.0,
      "text": "So I wanted to show you some of the iterations"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 377828.0,
      "end_time": 382421.0,
      "text": "we did between the first version, the Jaipur Knee,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 382421.0,
      "end_time": 384242.0,
      "text": "so this is it right here."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 384242.0,
      "end_time": 385968.0,
      "text": "(Clicking)"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 385968.0,
      "end_time": 388186.0,
      "text": "Notice anything about it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 388186.0,
      "end_time": 390746.0,
      "text": "It clicks."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 390747.0,
      "end_time": 393613.0,
      "text": "We&#39;d seen that users had actually modified it."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 393613.0,
      "end_time": 397125.0,
      "text": "So do you see that black strip right there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 397125.0,
      "end_time": 400117.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a homemade noise dampener."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 400117.0,
      "end_time": 402335.0,
      "text": "We also saw that our users had modified it"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 402335.0,
      "end_time": 403769.0,
      "text": "in other ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 403769.0,
      "end_time": 405559.0,
      "text": "You can see there that that particular amputee,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 405559.0,
      "end_time": 407788.0,
      "text": "he had wrapped bandages around the knee."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 407788.0,
      "end_time": 409512.0,
      "text": "He&#39;d made a cosmesis."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 409512.0,
      "end_time": 411708.0,
      "text": "And if you look at the knee,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 411708.0,
      "end_time": 415162.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s got those pointy edges, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 415162.0,
      "end_time": 417364.0,
      "text": "So if you&#39;re wearing it under pants or a skirt"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 417365.0,
      "end_time": 419625.0,
      "text": "or a sari, it&#39;s really obvious"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 419625.0,
      "end_time": 421221.0,
      "text": "that you&#39;re wearing a prosthetic limb,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 421221.0,
      "end_time": 425413.0,
      "text": "and in societies where there&#39;s social stigma around being disabled,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 425413.0,
      "end_time": 428370.0,
      "text": "people are particularly acute about this."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 428370.0,
      "end_time": 430686.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m going to show you some of the modifications we did."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 430686.0,
      "end_time": 433601.0,
      "text": "We did a lot of iterations, not just  around this, but some other things."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 433601.0,
      "end_time": 436290.0,
      "text": "But here we have the version three,  the ReMotion Knee,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 436290.0,
      "end_time": 437848.0,
      "text": "but if you look in here, you can see"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 437848.0,
      "end_time": 442566.0,
      "text": "the noise dampener. It&#39;s quieter."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 442566.0,
      "end_time": 446219.0,
      "text": "The other thing we did is that we smoothed the profile."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 446219.0,
      "end_time": 447651.0,
      "text": "We made it thinner."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 447651.0,
      "end_time": 449359.0,
      "text": "And something that&#39;s not obvious is that we"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 449359.0,
      "end_time": 452560.0,
      "text": "designed it for mass production."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 452560.0,
      "end_time": 454256.0,
      "text": "And this goes into my last point."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 454256.0,
      "end_time": 456227.0,
      "text": "We really, truly believe that if a product"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 456227.0,
      "end_time": 458563.0,
      "text": "is going to reach users at the scale that it&#39;s needed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 458564.0,
      "end_time": 460399.0,
      "text": "it needs to be market-driven,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 460399.0,
      "end_time": 463644.0,
      "text": "and market-driven means that products are sold."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 463644.0,
      "end_time": 466767.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re not donated. They&#39;re not heavily subsidized."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 466767.0,
      "end_time": 468980.0,
      "text": "Our product needs to be designed to offer value"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 468980.0,
      "end_time": 470281.0,
      "text": "to the end user."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 470281.0,
      "end_time": 472460.0,
      "text": "It also has to be designed to be very affordable."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 472460.0,
      "end_time": 474633.0,
      "text": "But a product that is valued by a customer"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 474634.0,
      "end_time": 476345.0,
      "text": "is used by a customer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 476345.0,
      "end_time": 478518.0,
      "text": "and use is what creates impact."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 478518.0,
      "end_time": 480277.0,
      "text": "And we believe that as designers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 480277.0,
      "end_time": 483507.0,
      "text": "it holds us accountable to our customers."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 483507.0,
      "end_time": 486123.0,
      "text": "And with centralized manufacturing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 486123.0,
      "end_time": 488150.0,
      "text": "you can control the quality control,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 488150.0,
      "end_time": 489878.0,
      "text": "and you can hit that $80 price point"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 489878.0,
      "end_time": 492368.0,
      "text": "with profit margins built in."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 492368.0,
      "end_time": 494524.0,
      "text": "And now, those profit margins are critical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 494524.0,
      "end_time": 496193.0,
      "text": "because if you want to scale, if you want to reach"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 496193.0,
      "end_time": 498452.0,
      "text": "all the people in the world who possibly need a knee,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 498452.0,
      "end_time": 501609.0,
      "text": "it needs to be economically sustainable."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 501609.0,
      "end_time": 504205.0,
      "text": "So I want to give you a sense of where we are at."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 504205.0,
      "end_time": 507781.0,
      "text": "We have fit over 5,000 amputees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 507781.0,
      "end_time": 510000.0,
      "text": "and one of the big indicators we&#39;re looking at, of course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 510000.0,
      "end_time": 511913.0,
      "text": "is, does it improve lives?"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 511913.0,
      "end_time": 513649.0,
      "text": "Well, the standard is, is someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 513649.0,
      "end_time": 516174.0,
      "text": "still wearing their knee six months later?"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 516174.0,
      "end_time": 518876.0,
      "text": "The industry average is about 65 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 518876.0,
      "end_time": 521169.0,
      "text": "Ours is 79 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 521169.0,
      "end_time": 524112.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re hoping to get that higher."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 524113.00000000006,
      "end_time": 527126.0,
      "text": "Right now, our knees are worn in 12 countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 527126.0,
      "end_time": 528736.0,
      "text": "This is where we want to get, though,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 528736.0,
      "end_time": 530254.0,
      "text": "in the next three years."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 530254.0,
      "end_time": 532754.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll double the impact in 2015,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 532754.0,
      "end_time": 535872.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;ll double it each of the following years after that."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 535872.0,
      "end_time": 537704.0,
      "text": "But then we hit a new challenge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 537705.0,
      "end_time": 539724.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s the number of skilled prosthetists"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 539724.0,
      "end_time": 542832.0,
      "text": "who are able to fit knees."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 542832.0,
      "end_time": 545513.0,
      "text": "So I want to end with a story of Pournima."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 545513.0,
      "end_time": 547160.0,
      "text": "Pournima was 18 years old"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 547160.0,
      "end_time": 550280.0,
      "text": "when she was in a car accident where she lost her leg,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 550280.0,
      "end_time": 553469.0,
      "text": "and she traveled 12 hours by train"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 553469.0,
      "end_time": 555896.0,
      "text": "to come to the clinic to be fit with a knee,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 555896.0,
      "end_time": 558488.0,
      "text": "and while all of the amputees who wear our knees"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 558489.0,
      "end_time": 560665.0,
      "text": "affect us as the designers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 560665.0,
      "end_time": 564932.0,
      "text": "she&#39;s particularly meaningful to me  as an engineer and as a woman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 564932.0,
      "end_time": 566496.0,
      "text": "because she was in school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 566496.0,
      "end_time": 569220.0,
      "text": "she had just started school to study engineering."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 569220.0,
      "end_time": 571375.0,
      "text": "And she said, \"Well, now that I can walk again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 571375.0,
      "end_time": 573783.0,
      "text": "I can go back and complete my studies.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 573783.0,
      "end_time": 576953.0,
      "text": "And to me she represents the next generation"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 576953.0,
      "end_time": 579985.0,
      "text": "of engineers solving problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 579985.0,
      "end_time": 582430.0,
      "text": "and ensuring meaningful technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 582430.0,
      "end_time": 584214.0,
      "text": "reach their users."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 584214.0,
      "end_time": 586252.0,
      "text": "So thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 586252.0,
      "end_time": 590550.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}